snippet.title: Coleco Telstar Ranger Pong Video Game 1977
snippet.description: The Coleco Telstar Ranger has four classic pong games and two shooting games. The light gun works just like the later NES Zapper, and it looks just like a Colt 45 revolver complete with cocking hammer. Accompanying retro Atari video game music is from the mind-boggling vgmusic.com . Please subscribe to our channel to see lots of cool old things that do stuff.
